doc.title: ukuhlela
doc.description: Ingcenye le imayelana nokuthi ungahlela njani

example1.title: {{0}}Isibonelo sekhodi yekhasi lasekhaya
example1.annotation1: Hlola bona libizo lesizinda elifanako na. Nangabe akunjalo, buyisela {{0}} begodu ungasasebenzi.
example1.annotation2: Hlola bona ngu-{{0}} nofana ikhasi lokuthoma lesiteshi. Indlela yayo ithoma ngephawu le-@.
example1.annotation4: Hlola bona lilikhasi elifitjhani levidiyo. Indlela yalo ithoma nge-/shorts/.
